Desktop Shortcut
\layout Standard

To create a desktop shortcut after running the Stepconf Wizard.
 From the CNC menu start EMC2 and pick your new configuration from the list.
 Check off Create Desktop Shortcut then OK.
 Now you can run your configuration from the desktop shortcut.
\layout Section

Modifying
\layout Standard

To change something in the basic configuration created by Stepconf Wizard
 run the wizard again.
 Select Modify a configuration...
 Then pick the configuration file .stepconf you wish to modify in the emc2/config
s folder.
 The file headers tell you if the file can be manually edited or not.
